WEBVTT

00:02:32.744 --> 00:02:36.735
Ruke uvis!
-Dole smesta! Zalegnite!

00:02:36.815 --> 00:02:40.005
Ostanite tu!
Nemojte da ste se mrdnuli!

00:02:40.085 --> 00:02:41.935
Dole!
