Idemo, idemo!

00:02:46.791 --> 00:02:49.080
Da se niko nije mrdnuo!

00:02:49.160 --> 00:02:53.485
Svi ostanite dole!
-Mnogo hvala,

00:02:53.565 --> 00:02:56.299
dame i gospodo.
